column5: I've accepted   invitation from my friend, to go to his cottage in deep woods and fish his private lake ( he did not has to ask me twice  ). After 4x4-ing last few km streach of the trail, we've arrived to the visible excitement of the black flies  View of the lake   For the first time I've had a"pikeless" fishing trip, but no complains. We've managed to catch other species to try few new recipes    Few bigger ones    After two days the change of diet was necessary, so we've switched to different species       One of the "visitors"    When we were leaving the lake was calm and peacefull again.
Nice report, thanks for sharing.  How did you get rid of that Porcupine?
Great report and that certainly looks like a really great lake to fish, with some quality fish!
Great report, looks like it was a beautiful place to spend a few days.  I don't think I would have stood that close to the porcupine myself tho  Joey
Looks like a gorgeuos spot, nice report!
Nice report Mark. Like others have said, that spot looks gorgeous!
nice report, looks like a greatplace to spend time in the canoe.  Hope ya didn';t try and pet that scragly looking kitty
wow---nice little piece of heaven there    way to go
You are right, it is heaven Some pictures of the same spot in winter
Great report K, must be absolutely great to fish places that remote. Looks awesome in winter too, whats the icefishing like.....do you have any pics....lol...sorry...i just love icefishing.
Great report, thanks for sharing. Makes me pine for my little getaway.
Nice fishing report & pics too !!!!!.  ..greaqt scenery too,it sure looks like an amazing lake,with lots of big fish to !!...cheers
I tried using "woda" once on a porcupine... damn thing wasn't even bothered by it and held its ground.  Fajne ryby
Nice spot, good peaceful fishing, can't beat it...
Nice fish.  Personally, I would have had used the phillips head on the porcupine, lol.  Wdzięczności za rozdzielanie.  reefrunner
nice fish....LOL , the bugs must have been brutal, as a suit like that doesn't come out unless its totaly untolerable !!!
